  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Difference between secukinumab and placebo in terms of joint synovitis as measured by the PDUS Global OMERACT-EULAR Synovitis Score (GLOESS)</measure>
    <time_frame>12 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>The primary objective of this study is to demonstrate that there is a difference between secukinumab and placebo in terms of joint synovitis response over 12 weeks as measured by the PDUS Global OMERACT-EULAR Synovitis Score (GLOESS) of the affected joints in PsA patients with an inadequate response (IR) to non biologic DMARDs.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
